          "description": "The staff were kind, and took my son in quickly.\nBut he had a chest xray as he very clearly had synptoms of pneumonia. They said his xray was clear. This morning, I received a call- almost 48 hours later saying they had misread xray-- and he does indeed have pneumonia!  He has been in terrible pain, with high fever.. This would have been avoided with a competent",
